    <h1>Virat Kohli</h1>
    Virat Kohli is a world-famous Indian cricketer known for his aggressive batting style and consistency. 
    He has led the team in all formats and is often called the <mark>run-machine</mark> due to his remarkable ability to score big runs. 
    He made his international debut in <pre>2008</pre> and has since become one of the top batsmen globally. 
    He holds records in all formats and is respected for his <code>work ethic</code> and <code>fitness</code>. 
    His leadership as captain helped India achieve many milestones. 
    He plays for <abbr title="Royal Challengers Bangalore">RCB</abbr> in the IPL and has a massive fan following.
    <blockquote>“Self-belief and hard work will always earn you success.”</blockquote>
